Name: Rag Doll Joe
About the game: Rag Doll Joe is a casual based game where you must toss the Rag doll Joe into objects on screen. OBJECTIVE: - Throw Rag Doll Joe into the objects on screen - For every object knocked off screen you will gain points - On achieving three stars you will proceed to the next level FEATURES TO COME: - Add additional Rag Doll characters - Additional levels - Character ( Rag Doll ) Customization - Achievements - And more!
